<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/8 (25 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Beast of Burden.</em></strong> The mule is considered to be a Large animal for the purpose of determining its carrying capacity.</p>

<p><strong><em>Sure-Footed.</em></strong> The mule has advantage on Strength and Dexterity saving throws made against effects that would knock it prone.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Hooves.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d4 + 2) bludgeoning damage.</p>

